{"tid":1012272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔小心夾親蝗蟲仔 依家即刻要去沖涼","createTime":"2019-02-07T12:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T17:22:59.000Z","uid":208536,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"770059c9cd93d143c48e13771de6592cbf994882","tid":1012272,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"話說因爲有公事要做<br />\n諗住舒舒服服唔想迫地鐵<br />\n岩岩係太子坐直通車番上深圳<br />\n已經專登揀個前後都未有人坐既位坐咗先<br />\n點知 臨開車個陣<br />\n有個大媽帶住隻蝗蟲仔坐係我後面<br />\n已經心知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一上黎唔夠2分鐘係咁踢我張櫈<br />\n本身都唔想理 佢越踢越過癮<br />\n踢到好似交響樂咁<br />\n我頂唔撚緊企起身望住佢<br />\n佢即刻停咗<br />\n<br />\n我以為可以安全渡過<br />\n點知 唔夠20分鐘<br />\n事關我坐左邊窗口位<br />\n我feel到左邊膊頭有野掂我<br />\n屌佢老母望一望嚇撚親<br />\n係蝗蟲仔隻手<br />\n佢竟然伸上黎望下 仲係到say hello<br />\n頭先睇完出面有個post樓主用背脊壓死隻小強<br />\n我都即刻用左手夾撚住佢帶埋耳機訓教扮咩都聽唔到<br />\n<br />\n然後佢喊 <br />\n佢老母望一望我又唔敢屌柒我<br />\n隻蝗蟲仔仲要俾佢老母屌鳩佢亂鳩咁郁身郁勢<br />\n我依家終於知個位樓主一下壓死隻小強係咩感受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdde5509465b27564feee3d1bb9c538e7511bc23","tid":1012272,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"巧得意丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6db4afbc90e970142fbd10be21dc0bb68e2b96","tid":1012272,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5eb7f0a5c51027233d1936567bb9702ddf9c7c","tid":1012272,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63df55894426af0eb2740b2aa090b13c43e6eff","tid":1012272,"uid":26752,